Package com.silabs.bluetooth_mesh

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BluetoothMesh
    BluetoothMesh class is the main class of the Android Bluetooth Mesh API, it is responsible to deal with all the objects, databases, connectivity, and also acts like a gate between the Silicon Labs Bluetooth Mesh Stack and this API
    BluetoothMeshNative
    This class declare all the inputs to the Native Mesh Stack C API abstraction layer.
    ConfigOperation
    Class that creates the object to be used during the configuration process
    DeviceInfo
    DeviceInfo is the class that defines and holds the devices/nodes information.
    ExportInfo
    ExportInfo class is responsible to create the JSON file from the NetworkInfo object.
    GroupInfo
    Class that represents a Group in the Mesh Network, it is responsible to provide all the variables according to the Bluetooth Mesh Specification
    ImportInfo
    Created by jcstange on 16/11/2017.
    MeshCallback
    This class is the only interface between BluetoothMesh and the user application.
    Model
    Model class is responsible to set the Bluetooth Mesh Model structure
    NetworkInfo
    NetworkInfo class makes the main object of the Bluetooth Mesh, the Network object, which holds all the information necessary to run Bluetooth Mesh
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ConfigOperation.Status
    Enum containing all the configurations error codes
